==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sparteine
<hw>Spar"te*ine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A narcotic alkaloid extracted from the tops of the common broom
(<spn>Cytisus scoparius</spn>, formerly <spn>Spartium scoparium</spn>),
as a colorless oily liquid of aniline-like odor and very bitter
taste.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sparterie</ent>⟦br⟧
